'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 23''' was the 23rd issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]'', released for [[November]]/[[December]] [[1999]]. It largely reprinted content from [[Star Wars Insider 46|''Star Wars Insider'' 46]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*[[Feel the Force]]
*[[Prequel Update]]
*[[Jawa's Corner|Jawas' Corner]]
*[[Star Wars Q&A|''Star Wars'' Q&A]]
*[[Prequel Profile]] &mdash; [[Paul Martin Smith]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 46}}
*[[Bookshelf]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 46}}
*[[Comlink (department)|Comlink]]

===Features===
*"[[Anthony Daniels: Nuts and Bolts]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 46|''Star Wars Insider'' 46]]}}
*"[[The Vehicles of Episode I]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 46}}
*"[[A Jedi Trio]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 46}}
